  "prompt": "Can I change the nominee details in Atal Pension Yojana?",
  "response": "Yes, you can change the nominee details in the Atal Pension Yojana (APY). To do this, you need to follow these steps:\n\n1. **Obtain the APY Nominee Change Form:** Visit the bank where you have your APY account and request the nominee change form. Some banks may also provide this form online on their websites.\n\n2. **Fill the Form:** Complete the form with the necessary details, including your APY account number, personal information, and the new nominee details.\n\n3. **Submit the Form:** Submit the filled form to the bank along with any required documents. These documents may include identification proof of the nominee and your own identification proof.\n\n4. **Confirmation:** The bank will process your request and update the nominee details in your APY account. You may receive a confirmation from the bank once the changes have been made.\n\nIt is always recommended to contact your bank for any specific requirements or procedures that may be applicable to your situation.",
